<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="foolishly-adv">foolishly <strong><em>adv</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'fuːlɪʃli/    美 /'fuːlɪʃli/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>傻地；愚蠢地：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Don't act foolishly.
别干傻事。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">真题解析</h2>
<ol>
<li>Well, you've acted <strong><em>_</em></strong>_ (愚蠢地) and you will pay for it.  </li>
</ol>
<p>答案：
1. foolishly / stupidly  </p></div>